author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be Microsoft delaying the inevitable. This is the year Windows 10 is scheduled to lose support and with people still not completely switching over, they've somewhat delayed the process. Why is this happening? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Microsoft Admitted They're Losing...
